WEBVTT

00:07:29.674 --> 00:07:32.867
or as fair, high-bosomed virgins.

00:07:33.939 --> 00:07:38.500
Yet all there is in the original Arabic
is that one word: houris.

00:07:39.245 --> 00:07:41.749
Not a swelling breast
or high bosom in sight.

00:07:41.773 --> 00:07:44.277
(Laughter)

00:07:44.301 --> 00:07:48.858
Now this may be a way of saying
"pure beings," like in angels,

00:07:48.882 --> 00:07:51.895
or it may be like
the Greek "kouros" or "kore,"

00:07:51.919 --> 00:07:53.261
an eternal youth.

00:07:53.285 --> 00:07:56.021
But the truth is, nobody really knows.

00:07:56.045 --> 00:07:57.289
And that's the point.

00:07:58.206 --> 00:08:00.622
Because the Koran is quite clear